    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-10-31T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-10-31T04:00:00-05:00" n="352"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d352">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 P.W./594: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-10-31T18:00:00+09:00"
                            >October 31, 1941—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 31—12:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1722. Continuing Embassy’s telegram No. 1721, October 31, 5 p.m.<note n="19"
                        xml:id="d352fn1">Not printed.</note> In summing up his interview with the
                    Minister for Foreign Affairs,<note n="20" xml:id="d352fn2">Shigenori
                        Togo.</note> the British Ambassador reported to the Foreign Office that he
                    believed that, while the Minister was genuinely anxious to bring about an
                    improvement in relations with Great Britain, he was chiefly preoccupied at the
                    present time with the situation in Southeastern Asia concerning which he is
                    probably under strong pressure and that, therefore, the time left for effecting
                    a solution of relations with Japan may be shorter than the Ambassador had
                    previously anticipated.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
